reviewText: My grandson loves this little sheep and it makes me smile to watch him as he watches Timmy. Timmy is adorable!

My son absolutely LOVES Timmy Time! He got addicted to it on Netflix and when they cancelled it, I didn't know what to do! Luckily I found it on Amazon! Thank you! Life Saver! Plan to purchase many more to add to our collection!
Really nice series, kids love it, wish it was longer. The repeat feature is nice to have. I watch it to.
This was a Christmas gift for my grandson. He loves racing & cars & Timmy so this was a great mix!

My granddaughter watched her first timmy time so much it was driving the rest of us crazy so we bought several more timmy times to give the rest of us a break. the little ones really love timmy, great for 3-4 year olds

My boys loved Shaun the Sheep but when Timmy Time came out they became hooked.  Timmy and his friends feature a preschooler version of Shaun the Sheep.  They get into fun mischief throughout this DVD in five short episodes.  It a cute DVD for any small kids who are looking for a break for typical animation.  They race go-karts, play sports and really just have kids fun!
My child loves this version.  Plays it so much, we've gone through 7!
My lil girl loves it bc all the animals
My boys can not get enough of Timmy.  They are current 3 and 2 but have loved it since about 1.5.
Fun for our three-year old and a good laugh for parents as well.
Item arrived as stated. New, good quality video and sound. Kid approved

Our toddler and preschooler love this show and watch it over and over.  There is no talking just the different animals making noises as they communicate.  If you like claymation then you will enjoy this.
